The '''[[Galactic City/Legends|''Galactic City]] civilian port''' was a port on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] that [[Ben Skywalker]] arrived after following a mission. The arrivals hall contained four ten-meter tall abstract statues on [[Marble/Legends|marble]] pedestals; ''Prosperity'', ''Progress'', ''Culture'', and ''Peace''.<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice">[[Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice]]</ref>

[[Mara Jade Skywalker]] picked him up at Arrivals 7-B.<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice" />

